data.description: The Meadows at Jodeco in McDonough offers luxury ranch homes with private courtyards. Gated living never felt so good. Minutes from he New Bridges of Jodeco, live, work play. Costoco, Boutiques, Movie theatres, minutes from I-75. Country living, city lifestyle. This Spectacular 4 sided brick home 4 BR, 3 full bath home has more to offer than can mention. Main level so spacious and open. Gated private courtyard is a focal point. with direct access from the family room, dining room and open kitchen area. 9ft. ceilings, hardwood floors throughout main level. In addition to a receiving sitting room near the front foyer - lots of windows, can be used as a home office, reading room, music room, very versatile. Enjoy the gas log fireplace as the center of the openness of FR, DR and Kitchen. The gourmet kitchen has two pantries, granite countertops, the bar has an overhang for barstools , recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplashes. Main level includes bedroom with full Bath across hallway. Master suite is private retreat with a sun/sitting room. Walk in closet, Master bath has great floor space. Oversized separate tile shower with dual designer sink.     Spacious upstairs has two large bedrooms with one full bath. the community is fenced around the perimeter, two gated entrances using key pad entry, owner must admit all guest. the community has great amenities including the saltwater pool, beautiful exposed beamed clubhouse and fitness center. You will appreciate the manicured lawns (grass cutting and lawn care included in HOA). HOA pays for water/sewer trash, exterior maintenance of dwelling, common area, termite bond of homes, and insurance. As you exit your two car garage and travel outside your gated community you are minutes away from everything. 20 minutes from Hartsfield Intl Airport, 10 minutes from Tanger Outlet, 25 minutes from downtown Atlanta. Schedule your tour today!
